title: Grateful Dead Live at Baltimore Civic Center on 1982-04-19
lineage: Anne Cohen : AD Transfer - Master Cassettes played on Nakamichi Dragon > HHB CDR830Plus > CD Ohr : CD > EAC > WAV > FLAC
description:

They Love Each Other

Peggy-O
Cassidy

reviews.review_text: This is the best aud available We should all hope that Ohr Weinberg keeps adding his work here because he made some of the most balanced and perfect auds ever. I noticed his stuff a few years back and grabbed everything available and was so stoked to see he's putting more out, and what a show my god ...

Perfect in way of good First off , echo previous review, excellent recording Ohr and Ann, thanks. This show was a wedding present from my friend, got married two days before. This was my last show for 5 years, starting a family and a small business kept me busy. I realize now that I was letting the perfect of shows I saw in late 70s get in the way of the all of the good of these early 80s shows. Just human nature , I guess. Re-listening to these shows via these flax fobs is fantastic, the transitions between the first fours tunes of second set are really great.  I know there are warts in these shows from this period, but they are so much fun listening now.
